<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们上了阁楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里又黑又脏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看见了可以玩儿的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“旧书！”艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“旧玩具！”哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗看了一下周围。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“角落里有鬼！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“世上没有鬼。”哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是你想象的。”艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是我想象的！”奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只是风而已。”哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去拿手电筒吧。”艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们拿着手电筒回到阁楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈利朝旧玩具走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他害怕地说：“少了一个！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不是风！”奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米看了看旧书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有本书也不见了！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个阁楼里闹鬼！”奥利弗说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米用手电筒照过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看到了一些毛。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鬼没有毛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈利用手电筒照过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看到了爪印！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鬼没有爪子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗深深地吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他朝着那个角落走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有东西在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它是……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗孚！”奥利弗喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗孚正在咬玩具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁边还有本书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗孚是跟着我们到这儿来的。”艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗拍了拍罗孚说：“罗孚也喜欢阁楼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
